## Description {#details}

A set of symbols and the their dependencies.

Used to describe dependencies for the <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/orc/materializationresponsibility/#ae3a8d9b6fd3d07c66e5992645636cc9b">MaterializationResponsibility::notifyEmitted</a> operation.
